title: Boy Band Manager Kenny Stops By
description:
His journey with Tayshia may be over, but Kenny is talking to Rachel and Becca about his time on "The Bachelorette" and why he came on the show in the first place. Kenny also reveals when he had a feeling that he was going to be sent home. 

Plus, Kenny plays a game with Rachel and Becca and reveals some secrets about his castmates, his time in Palm Springs, and Tayshia along the way.   

"Bachelor Happy Hour" has exclusive interviews every week. Watch "The Bachelorette" on ABC and listen to "Bachelor Happy Hour" the next morning. 

Don't forget to rate and subscribe so you never miss an episode.
